Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Bring a large pot of water to a boil. Lightly grease a 9x13-inch glass baking dish. Combine olive oil, Italian Baking Sauce, ricotta cheese, olives, Romano cheese, basil and 1/2 cup mozzarella cheese in a large glass bowl. Mix well. Cook PLUS(R) Elbows according to package cooking time. Drain and add to glass bowl. Mix well. Spoon mixture into a 9x13-inch baking dish. Top with remaining mozzarella cheese. Bake for 20-30 minutes or until cheese is bubbly.